{"tid":110493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"禁止未成年人0到8點期間打網游","createTime":"2017-02-06T17:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T01:51:41.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31d0c706084814f56d319503d3aec8cad1e08040","tid":110493,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:07:53.000Z","msg":"2016年9月，國家互聯網信息辦公室發布&ldquo;未成年人網絡保護條例（草案徵求意見稿）&rdquo;，並向社會公開徵求意見。時至2017年1月6日，該條例徵求意見稿最終形成送審版 在國家法制辦官網進行公示，並在一個月時間內徵求社會意見，不出意外，公示期結束後經人大審議通過，我國第一份&ldquo;未成年人網絡保護條例&rdquo;將正式出台，該條例具體 落地時間筆者認為可能會在今年以內。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/4unBxGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4unBxGB.png&h=808a3d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/6403ba64bd0d46013c8b24575532149d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F6403ba64bd0d46013c8b24575532149d.png&h=3259c9a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/7947a9ea35b2ee913468f9e2caa59279.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F7947a9ea35b2ee913468f9e2caa59279.png&h=53fdd155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前已經搞過網絡遊戲實名制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fb1f02c3155c273d4349be960dc25e40e338fa","tid":110493,"uid":59901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:13:22.000Z","msg":"禁止半夜打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843388ba1d153f07fef30c99f858597a0bfdb386","tid":110493,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:15:54.000Z","msg":"注意既係未成年人=未夠18歲既人<br />\n起之前既年代可以影響還可以<br />\n但起手機遊戲興起後大家可以見到既係愈黎愈多14,5歲既細佬仔開始打機<br />\n今次影響絕對好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8685db20a78efdb78a0b95e355e88c094c38a4","tid":110493,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/